================================================================================
üåê CYBERPUNK STYLE GUIDE
================================================================================

VISUAL LANGUAGE:
- **Form**: Futuristic, tech-noir, high-contrast neon aesthetics
- **Colors**: Deep dark backgrounds (#0a0e14, #181c20), neon cyan/teal primary (#2dd4bf, #06b6d4), electric purple accents
- **Typography**: Mix of futuristic sans-serif (Space Grotesk) for headings + monospace (JetBrains Mono) for data/code
- **Shapes**: Rounded corners (medium), glowing borders, layered depth with shadows
- **Interaction**: Glow effects on hover, smooth scale transforms, pulsing animations for active states

DESIGN TOKENS GUIDANCE:
- Background: Very dark (near-black with blue/gray tint)
- Primary: Neon cyan/teal with glow
- Surface: Semi-transparent dark cards with glass-like blur
- Radius: 0.75rem - 1rem (medium rounded)
- Shadow: Multi-layer glowing box-shadows (cyan glow)
- Animation: 300-600ms smooth easing, infinite pulses (3-6s)

COMPONENT PATTERNS:
- Buttons: Pill-shaped with gradient fills (cyan‚Üíteal), glow on hover, scale feedback
- Cards: Dark with subtle gradient overlay, border glow, glass morphism effect
- Inputs: Dark background, neon border on focus, glow effect
- Text: Use gradient text effects for emphasis, uppercase tracking for labels

LAYOUT & SPACING:
- Generous spacing (py-12, py-24, py-32 for sections)
- Centered hero layouts with large typography
- Grid-based dashboards with hover lift effects
- Background: Network grid patterns, ambient gradient glows (radial)

ATMOSPHERE:
- High-tech, cutting-edge, digital future
- Dramatic lighting with multiple glow sources
- Depth through layering and shadows
- Motion suggests energy and interactivity

DO NOT:
- Use bright/light backgrounds
- Use serif fonts extensively
- Create flat designs without depth
- Skip animations and transitions

================================================================================

